Note that if your cookie is not present with that exact name, your mechanism is skipped. Examining your `SecurityConfiguration` the filter is present in all requests so you need to either implement a mechanism to not add the filter to these unsecured endpoints or to add a method override to your filter so it does not activate on your unsecured endpoints:

    @Override
    protected boolean shouldNotFilter(HttpServletRequest request) {
        // your implementation
    }

One way would be using `request.getRequestURI()`.

